    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You hit them in the heart really hard, like directly in the heart. Make a Melee Taijutsu attack against a creature within range, on hit, the creature takes [weapons damage] +4d10, additionally, the target must make a Constitution Saving throw versus your Taijutsu save DC. On a fail, the creature takes a rank of Staggered and 3 ranks of weakened.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 2, increase the damage die by +6, if this jutsu is cast as a Chain 3, increase the damage die by an additional +2</p>",
